@startuml Safety Walk and Talk - Use Case Diagram (Clean)
!theme plain
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
left to right direction

' Actors
:User: as U
:Admin: as A
:System\n(Automated): as S

' System Boundary
rectangle "Safety Walk and Talk System" {
  
  ' === USER USE CASES ===
  
  ' Report Management
  (Create Report) as UC1
  (View Report List) as UC2
  (View Report Detail) as UC3
  (Edit Report) as UC4
  (Complete Report) as UC5
  (Update Status) as UC6
  (Delete Report) as UC7
  
  ' Dashboard
  (View Dashboard) as UC8
  
  ' History
  (View History) as UC9
  (Export PDF) as UC10
  
  ' === ADMIN USE CASES ===
  
  ' Master Data
  (Manage Areas) as UC11
  (Manage Departments) as UC12
  (Manage Categories) as UC13
  
  ' === SYSTEM USE CASES ===
  
  ' Automated
  (Send Email\nNotifications) as UC14
  (Send Reminders) as UC15
}

' === RELATIONSHIPS ===

' User to Use Cases
U --> UC1
U --> UC2
U --> UC3
U --> UC4
U --> UC5
U --> UC6
U --> UC7
U --> UC8
U --> UC9

' Admin to Use Cases
A --> UC11
A --> UC12
A --> UC13

' System to Use Cases
S --> UC14
S --> UC15

' Extend/Include
UC9 .> UC10 : <<extend>>

' === NOTES ===

note right of UC1
  Includes:
  - Upload photos
  - Select area, PIC, category
  - Set deadline
end note

note right of UC5
  Includes:
  - Upload completion photos
  - Generate PDF report
  - Send notification
end note

note right of UC8
  Displays:
  - Statistics cards
  - Monthly trends (line chart)
  - Area distribution (bar chart)
  - Category distribution (pie chart)
end note

note right of UC14
  Triggers:
  - Assignment email
  - Edit notification
  - Completion email (with PDF)
end note

note right of UC15
  Cron Jobs:
  - H-2 deadline reminder (daily 08:00)
  - Overdue reminder (daily 08:00)
end note

note bottom of "Safety Walk and Talk System"
  **Current Implementation**: No authentication system
  All features are publicly accessible
end note

@enduml
